  "remarks": "Professor of Chemistry. Deported from Italy to Tunisia on 27 Aug. 2006.\nLegally changed family name from Aouani to Lakhal in 2014. Review pursuant to Security\nCouncil resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 22 Apr. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.  INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
